snippet.title: Drop Boy - Launch Trailer (Arcade Game)
snippet.description:
Drop boy is a fast paced pixel art action arcade game. It is the result of 5 years of procrastination. I hope you love playing it as much as I loved thinking about making it.

I guarantee that it is hard, fun, challenging and addicting. It has super blocky pixel graphics. What more could you ask for?

DOWNLOAD FOR FREE:
https://hapiel.itch.io/dropboy

This game was made by Daniel Simu

The epic original soundtrack was made by VECTRAX:
https://twitter.com/risu_ika
